ry abbess of Saint-Julien-des-Prés at Le Mans."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Ada de Ramerupt was born in 1048, in Montdidier, Moselle, Grand Est, France. She married Geoffroy de Guise in 1070. They were the parents of at least 1 son. In 1095, at the age of 47, her occupation is listed as fondatrice et abbesse de l'abbaye de liessies. She died on 28 January 1119, in Liessies, Nord, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, France, at the age of 71."},"et":{"1048–28 January 1119":"1048–28. jaanuar 1119","1050–1122":"1050–1122","1060–1121":"1060–1121","1070–1141":"1070–1141","1075–1136":"1075–1136","1075–1150":"1075–1150","1095–1138":"1095–1138","1048–1119":"1048–1119","avant 1095":"enne 1095","1121":"1121","1075":"1075","1141":"1141","1095":"1095","1150":"1150","1050":"1050","1060":"1060","1070":"1070","1138":"1138","1048":"1048","1136":"1136","1122":"1122","28 January 1119":"28. jaanuar 1119","about 1075":"umbes 1075","1119":"1119","Montdidier, Moselle, Grand Est, France":"Montdidier, Moselle, Grand Est, Prantsusmaa","Ath, Hainaut, Belgium":"Ath, Hainaut, Belgia","Guise, Aisne, Picardie, France":"Guise, Aisne, Picardie, Prantsusmaa","Ath, Hainaut, Belgique":"Ath, Hainaut, Belgia","Liessies, Nord, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, France":"Liessies, Nord, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"1048–28 January 1119":"1048–28. tammikuuta 1119","1050–1122":"1050–1122","1060–1121":"1060–1121","1070–1141":"1070–1141","1075–1136":"1075–1136","1075–1150":"1075–1150","1095–1138":"1095–1138","1048–1119":"1048–1119","avant 1095":"ennen vuotta 1095","1121":"1121","1075":"1075","1141":"1141","1095":"1095","1150":"1150","1050":"1050","1060":"1060","1070":"1070","1138":"1138","1048":"1048","1136":"1136","1122":"1122","28 January 1119":"28. tammikuuta 1119","about 1075":"noin 1075","1119":"1119","Montdidier, Moselle, Grand Est, France":"Montdidier, Moselle, Grand Est, Ranska","Ath, Hainaut, Belgium":"Ath, Hainaut, Belgia","Guise, Aisne, Picardie, France":"Guise, Aisne, Picardie, Ranska","Ath, Hainaut, Belgique":"